            <p class="base-aside-card__subtitle font-sans text-sm text-color-text leading-regular break-words overflow-anywhere
                line-clamp-2">
              
          Real SEO Results: 27 Leads from a Simple Content Strategy

Just implemented a targeted insurance coverage strategy for a Hawaii dentist client, inspired by Steve Toth.

The approach: Created 12 focused "Does [insurance] cover [dental procedure]?" articles by:
➡️ Getting the list of accepted insurances from the client
➡️ Downloading each insurance's coverage PDFs
➡️ Using Claude AI to draft comprehensive, honest answers
➡️ Emphasizing alternatives and next steps when procedures weren't covered

The results speak for themselves:
🗓️ 13 appointment requests
🤳 14 direct calls

... and most of these pages AREN'T EVEN on page 1 yet.

That's 27 total leads - all from answering real questions that potential patients are asking.

Imagine the impact if we expanded this to cover every procedure they offer.

What I love about this approach:
➡️ Creates content actual customers are searching for
➡️ Grabs searchers while they're actively researching how to pay
➡️ Converts at higher rates than generic pages (250% higher!)
➡️ Builds topical authority in their specific service area
➡️ Delivers measurable ROI ASAP

What content strategy is driving your best results right now?
        
            </p>

