          If your SEO strategy doesn’t include UGC,
you’re already falling behind.

In this clip from my podcast with Sam Page (ex-SEO Director at
Slack, ex-Amazon), he shared one of the most overlooked shifts in AI-driven
search:

“UGC is the new link building.”

While most brands are doubling down on
blog content, Gemini, ChatGPT, and Perplexity are surfacing content from
communities—forums, reviews, Reddit threads.

Because language models don’t trust
polish. They trust real conversations.
And Sam had a clear warning for SEOs:

“Once your competitor builds a strong UGC
moat, it’s hard to catch up.”

Watch the clip and listen to the full episode here →
https://lnkd.in/gKGHwPJG

#UGC #SEOstrategy #AIOverviews #PerformanceSEO #ChatGPTSEO #GeminiSEO #SearchLeadership

        
            </p>

