                line-clamp-2">
              
          📢 The 2025 Previsible State of SEO Jobs Report is now available!

After analyzing nearly 10,000 job postings from 2024, SEOjobs.com and Previsible teamed up to uncover what’s really happening in the SEO job market.

Here’s what the data shows:

📉 Fewer content SEO roles
📈 More demand for technical and leadership positions
📊 Salaries trending down — but not for everyone
🤖 AI and LLMs are actively reshaping job descriptions

This is one of the most comprehensive career reports ever created for SEOs.  The report is packed with:

✅ Salary benchmarks by title, seniority &amp; state
