            <p class="base-aside-card__subtitle font-sans text-sm text-color-text leading-regular break-words overflow-anywhere
                line-clamp-2">
              
          Educational email courses change how agencies warm up leads.

They're simple, scalable, and actually get read.

Traditional lead magnets rarely build real trust:

• PDFs get downloaded and forgotten.
• Checklists don’t drive meaningful action.
• Most leave leads stuck—not ready to move forward.

A 5-day email course fixes all that:

✅ Helps leads solve a specific, painful problem
✅ Guides them step-by-step toward a clear outcome
✅ Train leads to open and expect your emails
✅ Naturally leads into your offer without being pushy

Here’s how the structure works:

→ Day 1: Solve an immediate, painful problem
→ Days 2–3: Teach bite-sized parts of your core process
→ Day 4: Share a story or transformation to build trust
→ Day 5: Offer a strategic insight + clearly lead to your service
→ (Optional) Add a FOMO follow-up sequence to drive action

What you're doing is guiding leads toward a desired outcome. 

It's one of the easiest ways to build demand and trust at scale.
        
            </p>

